Rating: 3
This is a good winter soup and very filling. I used red potatoes to increase the tartness and substituted meat sausage for veggie sausage (Japanese dried and crushed chili pepper used for spiciness). The soup should cook for about 70 minutes to avoid overly firm peas. The soup had a medium thickness when hot, but firmed very quickly as the soup cooled.

