We really liked the flavor of this one - nothing fancy, just great comfort food. We used 2 Kielbasa links, and that was perfect for us. Added some sliced carrots for a little extra flavor and color. We'll definitely make this one again - perfect for when it's chilly outside. Leftovers were extremely thick - might keep a little chicken broth to dilute it next time.

